    <mj-section>
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0px">
          <h2 style="font-weight: bold">Process</h2>
          <p><a href="https://www.zdnet.com/article/russian-telco-hijacks-internet-traffic-for-google-aws-cloudflare-and-others/">Russian telco hijacks internet traffic for Google, AWS, Cloudflare, and others</a><br />
            &ldquo;Rostelecom involved in BGP hijacking incident this week impacting more than 200 CDNs and cloud providers.&rdquo;</p>

          <p><a href="https://blogs.blackberry.com/en/2020/04/decade-of-the-rats">Decade of the RATs: Novel APT Attacks Targeting Linux, Windows and Android</a><br />
            &ldquo;BlackBerry researchers have released a new report that examines how five related APT groups operating in the interest of the Chinese government have systematically targeted Linux servers, Windows systems and Android mobile devices while remaining undetected for nearly a decade.&rdquo; And people wonder why COBOL is still around.</p>

          <p><a href="https://landing.google.com/sre/books/">Building Secure and Reliable Systems</a><br />
            A new SRE-focused eBook from Google that&rsquo;s free for everyone.</p>

          <p><a href="https://www.redhat.com/en/blog/be-careful-when-pulling-images-short-name">Be careful when pulling images by short name</a></p>

          <p><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2020/04/08/business/zoom-video-privacy-security-coronavirus.html">Zoom Rushes to Improve Privacy for Consumers Flooding Its Service</a><br />
            The stories we will tell our grandchildren about Zoom&hellip; I can&rsquo;t wait. &ldquo;The risks, the misuse, we never thought about that.&rdquo; Eric S. Yuan, the chief executive of Zoom Video Communications.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

